{"tid":2132251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方於葵青區打擊三合會「收陀地」活動拘86人","createTime":"2020-07-30T09:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T11:30:46.000Z","uid":13745,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a8e7b3e95ee344ecb070b57427556cc171010bb4","tid":2132251,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:33:36.000Z","msg":"警方在葵青區展開反三合會罪行的行動，拘捕共86人，分別是55男31女，年齡17至74歲，涉嫌勒索、非法集結、在非法賭場內賭搏等。警方在行動中檢獲約63萬元現金或非法賭場投注的籌碼。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，區內今個月出現「收陀地」的勒索活動，主要涉及兩個黑社會社團，向一些正當的運輸業商戶，收取每日上萬元「保護費」，亦會派出大量黑社會成員「曬馬」，向商戶施壓、令他們害怕。警方又指，有數名被捕人士有直接參與「收陀地」活動。警方指行動仍然繼續，不排除有更多人被捕。"},{"pid":"1557e6284dffbfd0ed91edb6d7b4b652e9800bd4","tid":2132251,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ed112c7b8ca1bf74575a01d4ad370ceadc98bb0","tid":2132251,"uid":20222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:34:41.000Z","msg":"拉左1 蚊買地未"},{"pid":"c5ac1443492e9b34ba3242ddd3a8b1eb5815bbdc","tid":2132251,"uid":10626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1557e6284dffbfd0ed91edb6d7b4b652e9800bd4","tid":2132251,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:35:39.000Z","msg":"好撚煩，個個post都洗"},{"pid":"ac0d4c186d0f021fd727c324a64be73eb718ffce","tid":2132251,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd6830a9f43c82ff20c0753e5f77518bb64e5271","tid":2132251,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:36:37.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"2e8552fc4e20af98bdda96861a076096db50cd69","tid":2132251,"uid":227271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"差佬：屌你收我D陀地？"},{"pid":"5ca66630b008f617017126079700939aacad3613","tid":2132251,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5ac1443492e9b34ba